name: DeltaPay
overview: DeltaPay is one of the leading and fastest growing systems on the payment acceptance market. The company was founded in 1995 as a paging service supplier, but as the telecom market developed DeltaPay began to develop its mobile network, it started to collaborate with cellular operators. In 2002 the company’s specialists have begun to develop, and in 2004 commissioned the own system, which allows customers to pay for mobile communication, TV, Internet, housing and other services (more than 600 operators are available). Reliability and security of the payment system, as well as its convenience and efficiency, have appreciated the hundreds of agents and millions of users across the country. The company is headquartered in Moscow, there are regional offices in more than 60 regions including Altai, Krasnodar, Perm, Arkhangelsk, Leningrad, Rostov and Tyumen regions.
